    </form>
  </div> -->
  <div>
    <p style="width: 75ch">
      - The search form above submits a post request with a name of idNum. This name correlates with the query set up in the get request on the '/show view'. Instead of using the slug method, this is also viable.
    </p>
  </div>
  </ul>
</body>
</html>